##  AS-IS Process (Current State)

```text
[Guest Arrival]
      ↓
[Wait in Queue]
      ↓
[Manual Reservation Lookup]
      ↓
[Manual ID Verification]
      ↓
[Data Entry in PMS]
      ↓
[Room Availability Check with Housekeeping]
      ↓
[Room Allocation]
      ↓
[Payment Processing]
      ↓
[Key Card Issuance]
      ↓
[Guest Proceeds to Room]

**Pain Points**
Long wait times during peak hours
Manual and repetitive data entry
Lack of real-time room status
Dependency on housekeeping confirmation
Inefficient coordination between departments
